sequenceDiagram
    participant Buyer
    participant DALP
    participant Custodian
    participant Counterparty

    Buyer->>DALP: Submit DvP instruction (deposit token + security)
    DALP->>DALP: Validate KYC, whitelist & policy checks
    DALP->>Custodian: Lock deposit token in escrow
    Custodian-->>DALP: Escrow confirmed
    DALP->>Counterparty: Lock security token in escrow
    Counterparty-->>DALP: Escrow confirmed
    DALP->>DALP: XVP atomic swap — T+0 execution
    DALP->>Buyer: Security token delivered
    DALP->>Counterparty: Deposit token delivered
    DALP->>Custodian: Release escrow records
    DALP->>Buyer: Settlement confirmation + audit log
    DALP->>Counterparty: Settlement confirmation + audit log
